{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>《Invoice Master Plus》是一款專為自由工作者、中小企業主與顧問設計的專業帳單發票管理應用，它能徹底解決您在行動中管理帳務的煩惱，告別繁瑣複雜的傳統軟體。現在限時免費中，這款 App 讓您在幾秒內即可輕鬆建立、管理並傳送專業的 PDF 發票，大大提升工作效率，絕對是您不可或缺的行動理財夥伴。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/460x460bb-75-70.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>全面整合多項帳務管理功能</h2>\n    <p>它能快速生成專業的 PDF 發票與估價單，支援自訂 Logo 強化品牌形象。內建客戶與產品管理系統簡化資料輸入，搭配即時付款追蹤與財務儀表板，讓您的行動帳務管理高效又精準。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-128-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-129-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-130-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-131-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-132-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-133-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：Invoice Master Plus</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Business</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-20T03:04:49.108458+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":308,"images":7,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}